Content.title: meemalee
Content.name: meemalee
Content.bodyText: Hey Darren, if you're south of the river you must try Hong Van on Lee High Road. Their pho and bun bo hue is lovely, though you have to ask for herbs or they assume you won't want them. It's a lovely place, cheap as anything and they always look really startled when you come in - I think they don't realise that they're a restaurant :-)
